    "image_18.jpg": "PorterPicks 6:52 PM\nLATE NIGHT NBA SELECTION for TUESDAY NIGHT\nHOOPS\n\n⚡\nDETROIT PISTONS (-2.5) over LA LAKERS\n\n(3-UNITS) 💰💰💰\n\n7:40pm PST - NBC\n\nEveryone is taking the Lakers because it’s LaBron’s\nbirthday. However, the Pistons are aware of that and\nwill be motivated offensively to score points as they\nare coming off a 2-game losing streak and haven’t lost\nthree straight games all season long, plus the fact\nthey are coming off scoring only 99 points in their last\ngame which was their second lowest point total of\nthe season.\n\nRemember, the Lakers have a bottom-five overall\ndefensive efficiency and come off only allowing 101\npoints to the Kings. Prior to that they allowed 119 to\nthe Rockets, 132 to the Suns and 135 to the Jazz in\nthree of their last four games!\n\nThe PISTONS are also 19-7 ATS as a FAVORITE this\nseason as well and we know that when the public\nmoney is on LaBron James, the Lakers throw games\naway. Not having Reeves could be missed tonight if\nthey are going to keep up with this Pistons team\ntonight!\n\nDone reading? Check out other channels.",
