    "image_21.jpg": "Monday Whale Plays\nHeat +4.5 (NBA) ✅\n\nStraight Bet: 1 Unit\n1 Unit = 10% Bankroll\n\nThis is a read only chat",
    "image_22.jpg": "12/29\n02:05 pm\n\nNOVIG\n\nPOR · -142 Matched\nMoneyline\n\n4,500.00 -> 7,677.53\nAmount To Pay\n\nDAL\nPOR\n10:35PM\n\nShare\n\nID: 69e2a238313a Placed: 11:07AM\n\nUpcoming Mon, Dec 29, 7:30pm\n\nTrail Blazers ML\nPOR - DAL\n✅\n-142\n4500U",
    "image_23.jpg": "[NFL] Rams -7 (-115) ❌\n\n[NBA] Cavs +3.5 (-120) ✅",
    "image_24.jpg": "yourdailycapper\n@yourdailycapper • 20m ago\n\nNHL: 1 Unit ( 7:00 PM EST )\nSenators 3 Way Moneyline ❌\n\nNFL: 1 Unit ( 8:15 PM EST )\nFalcons +7.5 ✅\n\nNHL: 1 Unit ( 10:00 PM EST )\nCanucks Moneyline ✅\n\nTake them straight. 1 unit is supposed to be 1-3% of your betting\nbankroll.",
