### 8.1 Tennis

| Bet | pick format | market |
|-----|-------------|--------|
| Match Winner | `Djokovic ML` | `ML` |
| Set Spread | `Nadal -1.5 sets` | `Sets` |
| Game Spread | `Alcaraz +4.5 games` | `Games` |
