### 8.2 Soccer

| Bet | pick format | Notes |
|-----|-------------|-------|
| Match Winner | `Arsenal ML` | 90 minutes (includes injury time) |
| Draw | `Arsenal vs Chelsea Draw` | type: `Moneyline` |
